Package: survalis
Type: Package
Title: Interpretable Machine Learning Methods for Survival Analysis
Version: 0.5.0
Author: Imad El Badisy [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Imad El Badisy <imad.elbadisy@protonmail.com>
Description: A modular toolkit for interpretable survival machine learning. 
    Provides model-agnostic methods such as SHAP, PDP, ALE, surrogate models,
    and counterfactual explanations for any compatible survival learner.
    Also supports estimation of conditional treatment effects and causal 
    interpretation in survival settings. Fully compatible with custom survival
    learners returning survival probability matrices over time.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
